KURUSEDHI YE KU PERU NA T.B. JOSHUA

0:00:50.180,0:00:54.500
Claudia Esquivar Mexico

0:00:54.500,0:01:04.760
Ndakasvika pano ndiri muwiricheya nekuda kwengozi yandakasangana nayo umo ndakaminyuka pachiziso chegumbo

0:01:04.760,0:01:09.260
uye ini ndakanga ndiri mumarwadzo akanyanya.

0:01:09.260,0:01:15.180
Aiva marwadzo andakanga ndisati ndamboona kare saka ndakatorwa ne ambulenzi kuenda kuchipatara.

0:01:15.180,0:01:21.160
Pandakasvika kuchipatara, kurwadziwa kwaiva kwakanyanya, ndainzwa sokunge ndakufenda.

0:01:21.160,0:01:24.400
Vakatora x-reyi ndokundiudza kuti ndaifanirwa kuoparetwa

0:01:24.400,0:01:29.460
uye kuiswa pulasita pagumbo rangu, izvo zvavakati ndaifanira kushandisa kwemwedzi miviri nehafu.

0:01:29.460,0:01:33.420
Pakutanga, chiremba akati aida oparesheni.

0:01:33.420,0:01:37.220
Vakatora ma x-reyi uye vakaona kuti chiziso chake chakanga cha chavhunika.

0:01:37.220,0:01:43.160
Chiremba akasarudza kutsigira gumbo rake ndokuriisa mupulasita kuitira kuti asagone kurifambisa.

0:01:43.160,0:01:51.540
Chiremba akandiudza kuti handaifanira kufamba negumbo rangu rakakuvara, kwemwedzi miviri nehafu

0:01:51.540,0:01:59.660
nokuti kana ndikadaro, ndaizowedzera kukuvara kwangu; ipapo, ini ndaizofanira kuenda kunoitwa oparesheni.

0:01:59.660,0:02:04.960
Uyezve, vanachiremba vakanditaurira kuti mushure memwedzi miviri nehafu, ndaizoda rubatsiro

0:02:04.960,0:02:12.320
kuti ndikwanise kufambisa ne kudzorera gumbo rangu sezvaraive kare.

0:02:12.320,0:02:18.380
Ndakanga ndichishandisa wiricheya. Ndakanga ndisingakwanisi kuita chero  chinhu ndoga sezvo mumwe munhu aifanira kundibatsira nguva dzose -

0:02:18.380,0:02:28.060
kuti andigeze, kundipfekedza ne kundifambisa fambisa. Nguva dzose, ndaiva ndigere mu wiricheya.

0:02:28.060,0:02:39.300
Ndaifanira kunwa mishonga katatu pazuva kuti ndisanzwe marwadzo, zvisinei nekuti ndaiva ne pulasita pagumbo rangu.

0:02:39.300,0:02:47.260
Apo mu Porofita T.B. Joshua akandinyengeterera, ndakanzwa mufaro mukuru norugare.

0:02:47.260,0:02:55.940
Ndakanzwa huvepo hwa Mwari uye ndakavimbiswa mukati mangu kuti ndakanga ndatoporeswa.

0:02:55.940,0:03:02.140
Panguva iyoyo, ndakasimuka nechivimbo chakasimba, ndichipa rukudzo nekuvonga Mwari

0:03:02.140,0:03:04.700
nekuda kwe mu Porofita T.B. Joshua kuti andiporese.

0:03:04.700,0:03:09.440
Ndakasimuka kubva pawiricheya ndokufamba nechivimbo chakasimba ne mufaro mukuru.

0:03:09.440,0:03:14.380
Zvishoma nezvishoma, ndakatora nhano; ipapo, ndakatanga kufamba chaizvo.

0:03:14.380,0:03:19.700
Ati iye panguva iyo mu Profita T.B. Joshua akamubata,

0:03:19.700,0:03:22.800
akanzwa rugare rukuru maari.

0:03:22.800,0:03:28.060
Ne ushingi - akanga ane chivimbo chakasimba chekuti Mwari aizomuporesa -

0:03:28.060,0:03:31.160
iye akasimuka ndokutanga kufamba ne kusvetuka

0:03:31.160,0:03:33.820
nokuti Ishe vakanga vatomuporesa panguva iyoyo.

0:03:33.820,0:03:37.940
Mushure mekuporeswa kwangu, hupenyu hwangu hwachinja - Ndasununguka.

0:03:37.940,0:03:41.680
Ndakasununguka kubvira panguva iyoyo apo kurwadziwa kwakandisiya uye ndakakwanisa kumira.

0:03:41.680,0:03:49.020
Kwandiri, zuva rega rega izuva rekukudza nekupa kutenda kuna Mwari pane zva Akaita muupenyu hwangu.

0:03:49.020,0:03:54.140
Ndakatenda kuna Mwari, ndakavimba naye; kana Akazviitira ini, Anogona kuzviitira iwe.

0:03:54.140,0:03:55.740
Iwe unofanira kuva nekutenda;

0:03:55.740,0:04:00.000
iwe unofanirwa kuzivisa ne kutora kuporeswa kwako nokuti kuripo kwauri.

0:04:00.000,0:04:06.900
Mwari mupenyu; Ndiye mumwe chete zuro nanhasi. Anoda kuzviratidza Pachake matiri tose.

0:04:06.900,0:04:10.820
Kubvira pandakawana rusununguko rwangu, ndinogona kuita zvose!

0:04:10.820,0:04:18.160
Ndinogona kufamba uye kumhanya. Handidi chero rumwe rubatsiro uye handisisiri kurwadziwa zvakare kunyange kunze kuchitonhora.

0:04:18.160,0:04:25.380
Handinzwi kurwadziwa uye apo vanachiremba vakaona ma x-reyi angu, vakatadza kuzvibvuma zvachose!

0:04:25.380,0:04:33.420
Vakaona ma x-reyi ose ari maviri ye kare na yazvino mushure mekuporeswa kwangu uye vanachiremba vakashamiswa zvikuru.

0:04:33.420,0:04:37.020
Ameni. Rumbidzai Ishe!

